<span id="freeTextContainer11461225320184893345">Set on a Louisiana sugarcane plantation in the 1970s, <b>A Gathering of Old Men</b> is a powerful depiction of racial tensions arising over the death of a Cajun farmer at the hands of a black man.</span>

