<div id="review_106704926" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/106704926" />
    <a title="Jill" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1444762-jill"><img alt="Jill" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1249324773p2/1444762.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/106704926?book_show_action=true">Jun 11, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jill" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jill" href="/user/show/1444762-jill">Jill</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer106704926" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9240664772902271700">I loved this book! It’s like &quot;The Magnificent Seven&quot; transformed into The Geriatric Eighteen. It is both comedic and tragic, and I believe it deserves its status as a classic of recent American literature.<br/><br/>This is one of those books that made me so excited by reading it. It’s an ineffable feeling that hits you when you know you have come upon something really good. <br/><br/>Rating: 4.5/5<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText9240664772902271700" style="display:none">I loved this book! It’s like "The Magnificent Seven" transformed into The Geriatric Eighteen. It is both comedic and tragic, and I believe it deserves its status as a classic of recent American literature.<br /><br />This is one of those books that made me so excited by reading it. It’s an ineffable feeling that hits you when you know you have come upon something really good. <br /><br />Rating: 4.5/5<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="9240664772902271700" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
